[xwang233]: I can reproduce this slow GPU impl on CUDA 11 + magma 2.5.4 and CUDA 10.2 + magma 2.5.1.

Testing script
```py
x = torch.randn(4, 4, device='cuda', dtype=torch.float)
with torch.autograd.profiler.emit_nvtx():
    y = torch.inverse(x)
```

nvprof nvtx results:
```
